E652 -- A 6502 emulator (cpu only).

  WORK-IN-PROGRESS
  Just for fun.

To build:

  $ git clone https://github.com/numsqx/e652.git
  $ cd e652/
  $ make

Useful resources:

+ https://github.com/amb5l/6502_65C02_functional_tests
+ https://github.com/cc65/cc65

